data.name: HelpCommandModule_SendQueryHelp_Description
data.value:
Operations ra filters harulai combine garera pani queries haru banauna sakinxa.
Example ko lagi: `{0}sg n:5 d:3 y:1995-2005` prayog garera years 1995 ra 2005 bich ko hard difficulty ko 5 round vayeko session start garna sakinxa.

data.name: HelpCommandModule_SendQueryHelp_Operations_Description
data.value: `n:` - Euta session ma khelne round haru (dherai ma 10) `im:` - Image manipulation: pixelate garna `im:p`, invert garna `im:i`, oil-paint garna `im:o`, grayscale garna `im:g`, vertically flip garna `im:f` athawa dherai ekkai choti garna `im:p,i,o,g,f` (kunai pani combination) `nh:` - Hint haru banda garna `nh:1` `aggr:` - Anime list pragyog garda aggregation method change garna: sabai combined `aggr:union`, sabai list ma preset `aggr:intersect` athawa list anusaar baraabar sample size banauna `aggr:balance` (default)

data.name: HelpCommandModule_SendQueryHelp_Filters_Description
data.value: `d:` - Difficulty `d:0` dekhi `d:5` samma (`0` le difficulty filter disable garxa`) `y:` - Year `y:2010` athawa year range ko lagi `y:1995-2005` `g:` - Genre `g:action` athawa dherai ko lagi `g:action,-sliceoflife,!kids`, jaha `-` ra `!` le genre exclude gara (sabai genre ko lagi `{0}genres`) `t:` - Song ko type: openings `t:op`, endings `t:ed` athawa songs insert ko lagi `t:in` (`in` command `sga` ma maatra usable) `sl:` - Sample ko length second ma, 5 dekhi 30 samma (`{0}sga sanga maatra usable) `mal:` - MyAnimeList ko user anime list `mal:username` athawa dherai ko lagi `mal:user1,user2` `anilist:` - Anilist ko user anime list `anilist:username` athawa dherai ko lagi `anilist:user1,user2`
